CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 8, 1945, pg. 18, reads: "Happy Birthday - Little Betty Jean Tallis of 21 Tannehill Street is having a good time at a party given in honor of her eighth birthday. She is surrounded by a group of friends who seem to be enjoying themselves also. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of children wearing party hats, gathered around Betty Jean Tallis posed behind birthday cake on her eighth birthday, in Tallis home, 21 Tannehill Street, Hill District
